<font size=\"22px\">1. 抽奖消耗对应的金币或积分，每次抽奖.en-us:
<font size="22px"> 1. The corresponding Coins or points are consumed in the lottery, and the Coins or points consumed in each lottery will be put into the prize pool.

 note: the points are in the form of Coins, 100 points = 1 Coin.</font>

<font size="22px">1. 抽獎消耗對應的金幣或積分，每次抽獎消耗的金幣或積分都會放入獎池。

3. 中獎後，金幣立即到賬，可點擊查詢最近10局的抽獎記錄。
